l interactions, which allows for simple resolutions to\npreviously paradoxical results. We conclude that the complexities of life\nhistories, including social behavior and multicellularity, can only be\nunderstood in the appropriate multidimensional ecological context.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 19 Jun 2016 21:34:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-19"}
