 in ZFC M (T) data not observed\nso far by previous workers. We argue that the ground state of BiFeO3 consists\nof the coexistence of the spin glass phase with the long range ordered AFM\nphase with a cycloidal spin structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 20 Jun 2016 12:02:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-21"}
